{"tid":1323103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要戰場]繼罷睇cctvb, 第二步phone-in電台","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:06:01.000Z","uid":264079,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b27358ec81e4a26457f196b956bed190e32bc2ad","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"老老實實而家聽得電台嘅都係一班上咗年紀人士，文宣下一個目標，一定係霸哂電台節目嘅phone-in 時間，原因有四 <br />\nif you can&rsquo;t beat them join them (講緊媒體渠道)<br />\n<br />\n一。 大部分聽收音機嘅都係上咗年紀嘅人(當中𣎴乏淺藍，深藍，淺黃)，既然未必阻到佢哋夜晚睇cctvb吸收維穩資訊，佢哋上下晝係會開收音機做BGM，所以電台起到一定文宣作用，一定要用電台講返事實出嚟，如黑驚點打人，擾民，制衡返cctvb<br />\n<br />\n二。好多商戶無電視都會開收音機，文宣效果可擴大至戶客群<br />\n<br />\n三。大部分港台，商台節目主持都係黃底，會幫拖<br />\n<br />\n四。啲廢老懶得睇圖/字，講埋俾佢哋聽就最好，仲可以擺archive 上Facebook 重溫<br />\n<br />\n主力:<br />\n1.政府唔回應五大訴求<br />\n2.追究黑驚濫權(拍淋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，擾民<br />\n3.鬧返建制狗嘉賓<br />\n<br />\n以下電台節目都可以phone in 按時間<br />\n<br />\n商台雷霆881<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKU2s00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKU2s00.png&h=e507f13d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在晴朗的一天出發<br />\n星期一至五 08:00-10:00<br />\n電話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1872881</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台第一台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrXSQdX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrXSQdX.png&h=f6bbfb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千禧年代<br />\n星期一至五 08:00-10:00<br />\n電話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1872311</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港電台第一台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4Tbmi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4Tbmi0.png&h=7f71191d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自由風自由phone<br />\n星期一至五 17:00-20:00<br />\n電話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1872311</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一陣好同我打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645f573b6eb65a2c46fd8dc4889050ecf6ac1ae2","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71d3430348ed9a0d74015204adcbe731584b7b1b","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"一陣5點好同我打去"},{"pid":"3df2d4cf13177854e4021438a449742b7b03f7f8","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"唔可以無嘢講"},{"pid":"19925fec1a407fae07fcc5e5827b67e8c924fff7","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba58619e6c099963568f5f3ef5da911d2f781457","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"882511693bcace3b441dfd776a008f3c83ffeca4","tid":1323103,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d3430348ed9a0d74015204adcbe731584b7b1b","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"一陣5點好同我打去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c012f5f592d0f13f0c7aac7af11580005e85e8fe","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"霸air time"},{"pid":"33d7a9fed9fc1d89c5860b48e4e77106b0bf9051","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"打電話呀"},{"pid":"bf761ab82fb6b86505ab5da5c908d9679b5550d5","tid":1323103,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66974b87bf1cad499a20bcca06485b1ee4b525be","tid":